{
  "texts": [
    "This underscores the challenge posed by cross-project vulnerability detection and emphasizes the limited generalizability of current methodologies.",
    "The findings emphasize the need for advancements in methodologies capable of generalizing effectively across various projects, especially in cross-project scenarios.R4 -Cross-Project SVD with Diverse CWE-IDs.",
    "Zhang et al. [266] and Liu et al.",
    "[128] both proposed to use deep domain adaptation to address cross-project VD in C languages.",
    "Subsequent research avenues could delve into cross-programming language VD and explore cross-project VD for other programming languages."
  ]
}